### Beanstalk
* centric view of deploying 
* view of EC2, ASG, ELB, RDS, etc in one place 
* free, pay for resources
* three architecture models:
  * single instance deployment: dev
  * LB + ASG: great for production or pre-production web-app
  * ASG only: non-web apps in production (eg. workers)
* Beanstalk components:
  * application
  * application version
  * environment
  
